# The movement command to reach the nearest iron ore resource executed successfully.
# Now, I will harvest iron ore from this resource.

harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.IronOre), quantity=10)  # Harvest 10 units of iron ore from the nearest resource.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check the inventory after harvesting iron ore.
print(f"Entities on the map: {get_entities()}")  # Check the updated state of entities.
